resources NI(4)
notes
We conduct coordinated observations of various auroras with the EISCAT radar 
and ground-based optical imagers, to develop a method for estimating 
characteristic energy of pulsating auroral electrons. 
We will run the SP only when it is clear sky and geomagnetic condition is active.

run /kst/exp/ei/arc1/arc1 fm cp1 NI
enablerec



